'''三氟甲基五氟化硫'''，化学式 CF<sub>3</sub>SF<sub>5</sub>，是一种稀有的工业[[温室气体|温室气体]]。<ref>{{cite book |first= Richard P. |last= Tuckett |title= Fluorine and the Environment Atmospheric Chemistry, Emissions, & Lithosphere (Advances in Fluorine Science series)|volume= 1 |year=2006 |publisher=Elsevier |isbn=0-444-52811-3 |pages=89–129 |chapter= Chapter 3: Trifluoromethyl Sulphur Pentafluoride, SF<sub>5</sub>CF<sub>3</sub>: Atmospheric Chemistry and Its Environmental Importance via the Greenhouse Effect |doi= 10.1016/S1872-0358(06)01003-7 |editor-first= Alain |editor-last= Tressaud}}</ref> 它在 2000年首次在大气中被检测到。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Sturges|first=W.T. |author2=T. J. Wallington |author3=M. D. Hurley |author4=K. P. Shine |author5=K. Sihra |author6=A. Engel |author7=D. E. Oram |author8=S. A. Penkett |author9=R. Mulvaney |author10=C.A.M. Brenninkmeijer|title=A Potent Greenhouse Gas Identified in the Atmosphere: SF<sub>5</sub>CF<sub>3</sub>|journal=Science|date=28 July 2000|volume=289|issue=5479|pages=611–613|doi=10.1126/science.289.5479.611}}</ref> 三氟甲基六氟化硫是“超级温室气体”之一。以每个分子计算，它被认为是地球大气中最强大的温室气体，[[全球暖化潜势|全球暖化潜势]]是[[二氧化碳|二氧化碳]]的18000倍。<ref name=MS2008>{{cite journal|last=Suen|first=Martin|title=Trifluoromethyl Sulfur Pentafluoride (CF<sub>3</sub>SF<sub>5</sub>): A Review of the Recently  Discovered Super-Greenhouse Gas in the Atmosphere|journal=The Open Atmospheric Science Journal|year=2008|volume=2|pages=56–60|doi=10.2174/1874282300802010056|doi-access=free}}</ref> 这种化合物在大气中预测有800年的寿命。<ref>{{cite journal |journal= Journal of Hazardous Materials |volume= 149 |issue= 3 |year= 2007 |pages= 747–751 |title= The prediction of environmental fate for trifluoromethyl sulfur pentafluoride (CF<sub>3</sub>SF<sub>5</sub>), a potent greenhouse gas |first= Wen-Tien |last= Tsai |doi= 10.1016/j.jhazmat.2007.08.035 |pmid= 17884286 }}</ref> 然而，目前三氟甲基五氟化硫的浓度仍然不太可能对[[全球变暖|全球变暖]]作出可衡量贡献的水平。<ref name=MS2008 /> 三氟甲基五氟化硫气体在大气中的存在归因于{{le|人类对环境的影响|Human_impact_on_the_environment|人类}}，可能是[[碳氟化合物|碳氟化合物]]的制造产生的一种副产物， 源于SF<sub>6</sub>与电子设备和微芯片中使用的氟聚合物的反应，或在[[高压电|高压电]]设备中的SF<sub>6</sub>与CF<sub>3</sub>反应，形成CF<sub>3</sub>SF<sub>5</sub>分子。<ref name=MS2008 />它的化学性质类似[[六氟化硫|六氟化硫]] (SF<sub>6</sub>)。<ref>{{cite journal |title= Trifluoromethylsulfur Pentafluoride |first1= Gene A. |last1= Silvey |first2= George H. |last2= Cady |journal= J. Am. Chem. Soc. |year= 1950 |volume= 72 | issue= 8 |pages= 3624–3626 |doi= 10.1021/ja01164a084 }}</ref>

